1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,200
Here's what science actually says about mucosal immunity.

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:07,200
Mucosal immunity is our first line of defense against pathogens.

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:10,800
It protects surfaces like our gut, lungs, and nose.

4
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:15,200
Studies show that mucosal antibodies can neutralize viruses before they invade.

5
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:16,000
But wait!

6
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:19,600
Preliminary research suggests there's so much more to uncover.

7
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:23,600
Mucosal immunity could even be key in developing future vaccines.

8
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:26,400
Curious about how your body defends itself?

9
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:29,200
Hit that follow button for more science!
